{"tid":1719772,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔需要擔心民鬥民","createTime":"2019-11-14T07:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T07:57:15.000Z","uid":254123,"like":154,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"46f6c980884bfc9c045c7e984a2108a8b97004cd","tid":1719772,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:20:55.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子你都唔驚，驚班冇腦冇槍既烏合之眾？<br />\n<br />\n又要驚畫面唔好睇？<br />\n<br />\n好簡單兩個方向<br />\n<br />\n1. 大波man何妖領軍果啲一定有便衣狗埋伏，冇乜野就由得佢，收錢做野燒唔得幾多次錢。<br />\n<br />\n但如果夠人對方襲擊一定要還拖，佢地收錢的好怕死的！<br />\n<br />\n2. 好似平時咁，亦會有堆真心膠既藍絲搞事，平時神獸大家經驗好好就唔需要多講。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果啲散水休息失敗撚唔該死撚開。<br />\n<br />\n依家已經打開咗勝利既缺口，咪再係度散播失敗主義！<br />\n<br />\n民賤聯工賊會你地夠膽繼續出賣你班冇腦支持者，<br />\n煽動佢地被受傷既話，你自己睇路！"},{"pid":"0f3cee2ba2a87ef5d41fd51a00ba915b6eee3a6b","tid":1719772,"uid":254123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"We don&rsquo;t forgive.<br />\n<br />\nWe don&rsquo;t forget."},{"pid":"4531424f9a0c88ab86a0b63f66eea30d61624c21","tid":1719772,"uid":165840,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"如果夠人對方襲擊一定要還拖，佢地收錢的好怕死的"},{"pid":"cc8c81133d9367e77d7b4a4543e8a4dee386847e","tid":1719772,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80cfd1026fc43f2d5823aa39820d371d812220d","tid":1719772,"uid":232382,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"你唔好on9啦<br />\n建制發動緊文革呀，唔係街頭打鬥，呢場一輸香港倒退五十年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Es522YC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEs522YC.jpg&h=7ef3eee1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77ef8da75a3c028d139af36d5cd138c66b0bf278","tid":1719772,"uid":232382,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f80cfd1026fc43f2d5823aa39820d371d812220d","tid":1719772,"uid":232382,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy